1
00:01:44,880 --> 00:01:45,520
Silp.

2
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:12,740
Môžem sa ťa niečo spýtať?

3
00:02:15,860 --> 00:02:16,520
Áno.

4
00:02:19,700 --> 00:02:21,820
Prečo si chcel,
aby som našiel tých dvoch ľudí?

5
00:02:29,500 --> 00:02:30,420
Mám zvláštne sny.

6
00:02:35,100 --> 00:02:36,740
Sníva sa ti o niekom, však?

7
00:02:36,760 --> 00:02:38,960
Sorn mi o tom niečo povedal.

8
00:02:40,620 --> 00:02:42,240
Mávam tie sny už dlho.

9
00:02:44,940 --> 00:02:46,960
V mojich snoch vidím chlapca.

10
00:02:51,940 --> 00:02:53,660
Niekoľko rokov som toho chlapca hľadal.

11
00:02:58,560 --> 00:03:00,480
A konečne som ho našiel.

12
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:06,900
A od toho momentu...

13
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:10,020
sa mi snívajú tie sny častejšie.

14
00:03:11,480 --> 00:03:13,120
Sú detailnejšie.

15
00:03:14,300 --> 00:03:16,380
A výrazne dlhšie.

16
00:03:22,220 --> 00:03:22,920
Ja...

17
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:24,920
A ten človek.

18
00:03:27,260 --> 00:03:29,240
Zistili sme,

19
00:03:29,620 --> 00:03:31,640
že sú naše sny prepojené.

20
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:39,000
V našich snoch

21
00:03:40,860 --> 00:03:42,620
sa voláme...

22
00:03:43,900 --> 00:03:45,320
Korn.

23
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:48,340
A Intouch.

24
00:03:56,760 --> 00:03:58,960
Som si istý,

25
00:04:02,340 --> 00:04:04,740
že jeden z nich

26
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:08,080
spáchal samovraždu.

27
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:24,600
A teraz...

28
00:04:25,500 --> 00:04:26,500
si začínam myslieť,

29
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:30,780
že ja som bol...

30
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:33,340
Korn.

31
00:04:34,280 --> 00:04:36,080
Chlapec,
ktorý sa zastrelil.

32
00:05:23,880 --> 00:05:25,020
Silp.

33
00:05:26,820 --> 00:05:28,720
Môžem sa pozrieť na tú fotku?

34
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:02,580
Bude to iba pár fotiek.

35
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:02,980
Rýchlo.

36
00:06:03,100 --> 00:06:03,660
Dobre.

37
00:06:03,660 --> 00:06:05,660
Pozri sa do kamery.

38
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,140
Pripravení?

39
00:06:07,740 --> 00:06:08,980
Dajte mi nejakú cool pózu.

40
00:06:12,280 --> 00:06:14,800
Raz, dva, tri!

41
00:06:22,640 --> 00:06:23,260
Hotovo?

42
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:24,160
Počkaj.

43
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:26,220
Ešte jednu, prosím.

44
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:27,870
Nehýb sa.

45
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:29,720
Nebol som pripravený!

46
00:06:30,020 --> 00:06:32,000
Raz, dva, tri.

47
00:06:34,420 --> 00:06:35,160
Hotovo.

48
00:06:35,160 --> 00:06:36,100
To je všetko, však?

49
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:40,880
Vyvolaj mi film, prosím ťa.

50
00:07:11,820 --> 00:07:14,060
Chlapec na tejto fotke sa volá Intouch.

51
00:07:14,060 --> 00:07:16,610
Zabil sa keď mal osemnásť rokov.

52
00:07:16,620 --> 00:07:19,080
Mesiac potom,
ako táto fotka vznikla.

53
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:23,840
Zabil sa...

54
00:07:24,440 --> 00:07:26,320
keď mal osemnásť rokov?

55
00:07:27,880 --> 00:07:30,020
Zle si to pamätáš.

56
00:07:34,640 --> 00:07:36,540
Tí ľudia, ktorých si chcel,
aby som našiel...

57
00:07:36,540 --> 00:07:38,120
Obaja spáchali samovraždu.

58
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:40,120
V ten istý deň.

59
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:47,360
Ujasním ti to.

60
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:50,240
Korn sa zabil, ako prvý.

61
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:52,800
Intouch ho hneď nasledoval.

62
00:08:10,860 --> 00:08:14,920
Intouch Chatphokin.

63
00:08:16,960 --> 00:08:19,640
Hovorí ti to priezvisko niečo?

64
00:08:34,679 --> 00:08:36,399
Na niečo sa ťa spýtam.

65
00:08:36,400 --> 00:08:39,860
Poznáš Antiku Chatphokin?

66
00:08:46,940 --> 00:08:50,240
Vieš, ako sa volala
tvoja mama za slobodna?

67
00:08:52,180 --> 00:08:55,780
Alin Chatphokin.

68
00:08:58,340 --> 00:09:01,500
Antika je tvoja stará mama.

69
00:09:02,040 --> 00:09:05,660
Ten chlapec na fotke
bol brat tvojej starej mamy.

70
00:09:05,660 --> 00:09:08,420
Je to tvoj prastrýko.

71
00:09:35,880 --> 00:09:37,220
Intouch.

72
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:45,240
Parm.

73
00:09:59,800 --> 00:10:00,940
Korn.

74
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:05,080
Áno?

75
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:08,220
Nebude to dlho trvať

76
00:10:08,260 --> 00:10:10,560
a budeme môcť byť spolu.

77
00:10:32,920 --> 00:10:33,840
Áno.

78
00:10:35,140 --> 00:10:37,840
Nebude to dlho trvať.

79
00:10:42,860 --> 00:10:44,740
Tvoj dáždnik.

80
00:10:44,740 --> 00:10:47,480
Je príliš veľký a ťažký.

81
00:10:47,490 --> 00:10:49,700
Môj dáždnik je pre nás
tá najlepšia možnosť.

82
00:10:52,280 --> 00:10:54,420
Dovoľ mi postarať sa o teba.

83
00:11:03,740 --> 00:11:06,340
Ale ak budeš so mnou,

84
00:11:06,340 --> 00:11:09,120
budeš musieť čeliť zlým veciam.

85
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:11,120
Preto ma musíš mať po svojom boku.

86
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:16,100
Ak budem pri tebe,
prinesiem ti šťastie.

87
00:11:17,700 --> 00:11:19,820
Urobím ťa šťastným.

88
00:11:21,680 --> 00:11:24,780
Je toľko vecí,
ktoré sme ešte spolu nerobili.

89
00:11:25,640 --> 00:11:27,280
Ver mi.

90
00:11:30,400 --> 00:11:32,180
Milujem ťa.

91
00:11:32,400 --> 00:11:34,180
Nie!

92
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:38,200
Korn!

93
00:12:03,780 --> 00:12:05,820
Milujem ťa.

94
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:21,960
Korn.

95
00:12:24,920 --> 00:12:26,600
Bože, Korn!

96
00:12:31,780 --> 00:12:32,820
Korn!

97
00:12:42,180 --> 00:12:44,320
Bastard!

98
00:12:46,520 --> 00:12:48,400
Hlupák!

99
00:13:01,760 --> 00:13:04,540
Ty hlúpy bastard!

100
00:13:18,340 --> 00:13:20,840
Parm.

101
00:13:30,040 --> 00:13:32,520
Parm, počkaj na mňa.

102
